in a two-man submarine.

31:13.414 --> 31:16.247
The pulverized acromion
is the important part
of that book.

31:16.333 --> 31:17.994
Well, you know what?
I like the sub.

31:18.085 --> 31:20.918
I can hardly wait to see
what you three
are looking for.

31:21.005 --> 31:22.745
Come on.
You gotta be kidding me.

31:22.840 --> 31:26.207
- You own a gun, Mr, Oeraﬂ'cki?
