on a concealed-weapon charge?
That was a mistake.

31:33.768 --> 31:35.884
I accidentally put it
in my pocket, you know,
when I left work.

31:35.978 --> 31:38.185
Can we see the gun please?

31:38.272 --> 31:40.263
She’s right over here.

31:40.357 --> 31:43.690
Uh-uh, uh-uh.
Real easy there, pal.

31:43.778 --> 31:46.110
We don’t want
any sudden movements.
No mistakes.

31:46.197 --> 31:48.688
- That’s it.
